UNITED STATES FIDELITY & GUARANTY COMPANY v. FIRST NATIONAL BANK, McALESTER, OKLAHOMA. No. 6095. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Aug. 13, 1959. Fite & Robinson, Muskogee, Okl., for appellant. Arnote, Arnote & Bratton, McAlester, Okl., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS and BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed pursuant to stipulation of the parties.
